## type ErrUnexpectedStatus

ErrUnexpectedStatus is returned if a registry API request returned with unexpected HTTP status

```go
type ErrUnexpectedStatus struct {
    Status                    string
    StatusCode                int
    Body                      []byte
    RequestURL, RequestMethod string
}
```
